WEBVTT

00:00:03.900 --> 00:00:05.000
were thrust upon me,

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.266
my whole world
has changed.

00:00:07.266 --> 00:00:08.567
Now I'm Ichigo Kuraski,

00:00:08.567 --> 00:00:09.967
substitute Soul Reaper.

00:00:09.967 --> 00:00:12.433
And I'm combining
my powerful spirit energy

00:00:12.433 --> 00:00:16.033
with this blade in order to
protect my friends!

00:00:16.033 --> 00:00:18.200
[♪♪♪]

00:00:20.934 --> 00:00:23.000
[WOMAN SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:01:48.900 --> 00:01:50.266
Take her and go!

00:01:50.266 --> 00:01:51.834
Get her to safety!

00:01:51.834 --> 00:01:53.667
Take her far away
from here.

00:01:53.667 --> 00:01:55.166
Huh?

00:01:56.533 --> 00:01:58.000
That's your duty.

00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.800
Protect her with
your life.

00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:07.333
Renji.

00:02:09.133 --> 00:02:11.100
[GRUNTING]

00:02:11.100 --> 00:02:12.667
Renji?

00:02:12.667 --> 00:02:14.667
Don't just stand there watching,
you fool.

00:02:14.667 --> 00:02:17.834
Go!
All lieutenants after them!

00:02:17.834 --> 00:02:19.100
Mm.

00:02:19.100 --> 00:02:20.467
Yes, sir.

00:02:22.133 --> 00:02:23.433
Go ahead.

00:02:23.433 --> 00:02:24.834
Right.

00:02:26.367 --> 00:02:28.133
[PANTING]

00:02:32.033 --> 00:02:33.333
[ALL GASPING]

00:02:42.133 --> 00:02:43.467
Now run!

00:02:43.467 --> 00:02:44.834
Itegumo!

00:02:44.834 --> 00:02:47.033
Bite.

00:02:47.033 --> 00:02:49.300
Gonryomaru.

00:02:49.300 --> 00:02:50.767
Crush him!

00:02:50.767 --> 00:02:52.633
Gegetsuburi!

00:02:53.600 --> 00:02:55.066
[GRUNTING]

00:02:56.600 --> 00:02:58.300
[GASPS]

00:02:59.500 --> 00:03:00.934
[GRUNTS]

00:03:01.734 --> 00:03:03.567
Huh?

00:03:04.500 --> 00:03:05.667
It's impossible.

00:03:05.667 --> 00:03:08.533
He's not even using
his Zanpakuto.

00:03:09.467 --> 00:03:11.133
[GRUNTING]

00:03:19.834 --> 00:03:22.433
[GRUNTING]

00:03:24.166 --> 00:03:26.300
I can see your moves,

00:03:26.300 --> 00:03:28.700
Byakuya Kuchiki.

00:03:39.367 --> 00:03:40.800
Tell me why.

00:03:40.800 --> 00:03:42.834
Hm?

00:03:42.834 --> 00:03:45.800
Why don't you
just give up?

00:03:45.800 --> 00:03:48.367
You keep trying to save Rukia
again and again.

00:03:52.233 --> 00:03:54.033
You're her brother,
aren't you?

00:03:54.033 --> 00:03:56.900
So the question that
needs to be asked...

00:03:58.734 --> 00:04:01.100
Is why the hell aren't you
trying to save her?

00:04:03.734 --> 00:04:05.533
Such a foolish question.

00:04:05.533 --> 00:04:08.367
Even if I did have
the time to try to explain

00:04:08.367 --> 00:04:10.433
the principle to you,

00:04:10.433 --> 00:04:13.233
someone like you would
never understand it.

00:04:16.633 --> 00:04:19.233
It seems talking
serves no purpose.

00:04:19.800 --> 00:04:21.533
Prepare to die.

00:04:23.767 --> 00:04:26.333
[GRUNTING]

00:04:31.233 --> 00:04:32.834
Ah!

00:04:35.533 --> 00:04:37.233
[BOOMING]

00:04:50.367 --> 00:04:54.066
There is only
one path before me.

00:04:55.900 --> 00:04:58.934
I shall kill you,
Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:04:58.934 --> 00:05:00.934
And then, once again,

00:05:00.934 --> 00:05:03.467
I will capture Rukia.

00:05:03.467 --> 00:05:04.934
And this time,

00:05:04.934 --> 00:05:07.333
I shall execute her myself.

00:05:07.333 --> 00:05:09.367
I won't let you
do that.

00:05:15.734 --> 00:05:17.767
That's the reason why
I'm here.

00:05:25.233 --> 00:05:26.667
[GRUNTING]

00:05:27.533 --> 00:05:30.100
RUKIA:
Renji, stop!
Put me down.

00:05:30.100 --> 00:05:32.934
I've got to go back there
and help Ichigo.

00:05:32.934 --> 00:05:35.367
What part of our running
like hell for our lives

00:05:35.367 --> 00:05:36.700
do you not understand?

00:05:36.700 --> 00:05:39.266
Just try to keep that big
mouth of yours shut, all right?

00:05:39.266 --> 00:05:42.066
We don't want anybody hearing
our voices!

00:05:42.066 --> 00:05:45.400
If one of our voices gets
us caught, it won't be mine.

00:05:47.433 --> 00:05:49.066
RENJI:
Explain something to me.

00:05:49.066 --> 00:05:50.400
RUKIA:
What?

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:51.500
Well, one time,

00:05:51.500 --> 00:05:54.500
Ichigo told me that
he owed you a favor.

00:05:55.266 --> 00:05:57.934
He owes a favor to me?

00:05:57.934 --> 00:05:59.367
RENJI:
Uh-huh.

00:06:00.667 --> 00:06:01.734
You know,

00:06:01.734 --> 00:06:04.800
Rukia actually saved
my life in a way.

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.633
She changed my destiny.

00:06:08.633 --> 00:06:10.900
That much is true.

00:06:10.900 --> 00:06:13.100
ICHIGO:
If I hadn't met Rukia,

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:15.300
I never would have become
a Soul Reaper,

00:06:15.300 --> 00:06:17.934
the ability I have
to fight the way I do,

00:06:17.934 --> 00:06:20.467
and to be able
to protect everyone.

00:06:20.467 --> 00:06:22.467
I owe her.

00:06:27.100 --> 00:06:28.433
RUKIA:
Because of me,

00:06:28.433 --> 00:06:30.600
Ichigo's fate
has been changed.

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:33.533
I've put him
in terrible danger.

00:06:33.533 --> 00:06:36.834
And nothing I do can ever make
amends for that.

00:06:39.233 --> 00:06:41.633
Why are you blaming yourself
for everything?

00:06:41.633 --> 00:06:42.934
It's pointless.

00:06:42.934 --> 00:06:45.100
You've always been
like that.

00:06:45.100 --> 00:06:47.367
No one else thinks
this is all your fault.

00:06:47.367 --> 00:06:49.633
So why don't you quit being
so hard on yourself?

00:06:50.834 --> 00:06:52.734
No one person could
be strong enough

00:06:52.734 --> 00:06:54.567
to carry all of
that responsibility

00:06:54.567 --> 00:06:55.767
on their shoulders.

00:06:55.767 --> 00:06:57.266
Certainly not you,
Rukia.

00:07:01.700 --> 00:07:04.533
Share it.

00:07:04.533 --> 00:07:07.934
Share that burden with
Ichigo and with me.

00:07:07.934 --> 00:07:11.600
Let us lighten your load until
you get your strength back.

00:07:11.600 --> 00:07:14.934
That is the whole reason we
both made ourselves stronger.

00:07:16.433 --> 00:07:19.700
Just have a little
faith in him, Rukia.

00:07:24.367 --> 00:07:26.133
Huh?

00:07:28.734 --> 00:07:30.800
RUKIA:
I'm sorry, Renji.

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:32.266
RENJI:
Don't be foolish.

00:07:32.266 --> 00:07:35.500
You don't have anything
to apologize for.

00:07:37.333 --> 00:07:38.767
Thank you.

00:07:38.767 --> 00:07:40.266
Hm.

00:07:40.266 --> 00:07:42.033
Silly girl.

00:07:42.033 --> 00:07:44.767
There's no need to say
thank you, either.

00:07:50.667 --> 00:07:52.367
KIYONE:
Isane.

00:07:58.967 --> 00:08:00.367
Isane!

00:08:00.367 --> 00:08:04.266
Wait, Kiyone!
Don't!

00:08:04.266 --> 00:08:06.467
Ah!

00:08:18.767 --> 00:08:20.533
Hold it,
Soi Fon!

00:08:20.533 --> 00:08:22.166
[PANTING]

00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:26.667
[GASPING]

00:08:32.700 --> 00:08:34.367
No one move.

00:08:35.400 --> 00:08:37.400
But Captain Yamamoto.

00:08:39.333 --> 00:08:40.633
This crime...

00:08:40.633 --> 00:08:43.767
A lieutenant freeing
a convicted criminal

00:08:43.767 --> 00:08:46.633
and aiding in her escape
will be solved

00:08:46.633 --> 00:08:48.500
by capturing
the treasonous officer

00:08:48.500 --> 00:08:50.967
and putting him
to death.

00:08:50.967 --> 00:08:53.533
Thus,
his fate is sealed.

00:08:53.533 --> 00:08:56.033
But that is the least
of our problems.

00:08:56.033 --> 00:08:58.233
What you two captains
have done here today

00:08:58.233 --> 00:09:00.767
is a crime of far
greater magnitude.

00:09:00.767 --> 00:09:05.433
Surely you both understand that
your actions are unforgivable!

00:09:09.667 --> 00:09:12.133
[GASPS]
Captain Ukitake.

00:09:12.133 --> 00:09:13.867
You're in danger, Captain.
Get--

00:09:13.867 --> 00:09:15.266
Kiyone,
stay back!

00:09:15.266 --> 00:09:17.066
[GASPS]

00:09:26.700 --> 00:09:29.066
Well, guess we've
got no choice.

00:09:29.066 --> 00:09:31.200
Are you ready,
Jushiro?

00:09:31.200 --> 00:09:33.834
Looks like we're gonna have
to make a run for it.

00:09:36.033 --> 00:09:38.700
Oh, Shunsui.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:42.934
UKITAKE:
Wait, Shunsui!

00:09:42.934 --> 00:09:44.567
I can't abandon
my squad!

00:09:44.567 --> 00:09:46.734
KYORAKU:
Just calm down.

00:09:46.734 --> 00:09:48.700
Did you really want to fight
old man Yama

00:09:48.700 --> 00:09:50.533
with all those
others around?

00:09:50.533 --> 00:09:53.600
If we did that, a lot of people
would have ended up dead.

00:09:54.667 --> 00:09:57.300
Now it's only
the two of us...

00:09:57.300 --> 00:09:59.700
For the moment.

00:09:59.700 --> 00:10:01.233
Can't you feel it?

00:10:01.233 --> 00:10:04.100
There's one more on our side
who's getting closer.

00:10:05.800 --> 00:10:07.500
You'd better concentrate.

00:10:07.500 --> 00:10:09.266
We're almost to
the ground.

00:10:10.667 --> 00:10:12.600
Oh, Captain.

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:15.433
How dare you stand there and
do nothing while they get away.

00:10:16.266 --> 00:10:17.934
[GRUNTING]

00:10:19.533 --> 00:10:21.500
[GASPING]

00:10:21.500 --> 00:10:23.700
Traitorous scum.

00:10:23.700 --> 00:10:25.467
With your
filthy treason,

00:10:25.467 --> 00:10:27.066
you and your
bastard captain

00:10:27.066 --> 00:10:28.700
and all the others
have brought shame

00:10:28.700 --> 00:10:30.700
on the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:10:30.700 --> 00:10:33.367
Ah!

00:10:33.367 --> 00:10:35.000
But rest assured,

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:37.734
I'm going to put you
out of your misery.

00:10:37.734 --> 00:10:40.533
You will never betray
anyone ever again,

00:10:40.533 --> 00:10:42.367
once you're dead!

00:10:43.300 --> 00:10:45.266
Ah!

00:10:51.633 --> 00:10:55.166
[♪♪♪]

00:10:58.500 --> 00:11:00.500
[GRUNTING]

00:11:03.734 --> 00:11:05.033
[GRUNTING]

00:11:05.033 --> 00:11:06.367
Let go of me!

00:11:06.367 --> 00:11:08.200
And who the hell are you,
anyway?

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:09.533
Such a fuss.

00:11:09.533 --> 00:11:11.200
I see you
haven't changed.

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:14.467
You have a quick temper,
just like you always used to.

00:11:15.934 --> 00:11:18.033
It can't be you.

00:11:25.633 --> 00:11:27.266
It can't be you.

00:11:28.800 --> 00:11:30.233
Yoruichi.

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:34.667
Well, long time no see,
Sui-Feng.

00:11:37.700 --> 00:11:39.133
[GRUNTS]

00:11:42.333 --> 00:11:44.867
[BOOMING]

00:11:49.567 --> 00:11:51.800
[GRUNTING]

00:11:51.800 --> 00:11:53.967
How are you feeling,
Isane?

00:11:53.967 --> 00:11:55.367
Any pain?

00:11:55.367 --> 00:11:58.100
[GASPS]
Captain, I'm so sorry.

00:11:58.100 --> 00:11:59.266
The Ryoka was ju--

00:11:59.266 --> 00:12:00.700
UNOHANA:
Easy, easy.

00:12:00.700 --> 00:12:02.400
It's all right,
Isane.

00:12:02.400 --> 00:12:04.734
You were not hit as hard as
the others,

00:12:04.734 --> 00:12:06.200
but you still
mustn't move around

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.867
too much until
you've recovered.

00:12:09.767 --> 00:12:12.300
Take us down now,
Minazuki.

00:12:12.300 --> 00:12:14.700
[WAILING]

00:12:24.934 --> 00:12:26.567
[BOOMING]

00:12:26.567 --> 00:12:29.100
[WAILING]

00:12:29.100 --> 00:12:30.834
Captain, we just heard
what happened.

00:12:30.834 --> 00:12:32.166
Is the Lieutenant
injured?

00:12:32.166 --> 00:12:33.767
Were you hurt too,
ma'am?

00:12:33.767 --> 00:12:35.233
What are your orders?

00:12:35.767 --> 00:12:37.133
We're all right.

00:12:37.133 --> 00:12:39.633
Release the others
and return, Minazuki.

00:12:46.066 --> 00:12:49.467
[GROANING]

00:12:59.900 --> 00:13:02.900
Most of their wounds are not
life threatening.

00:13:02.900 --> 00:13:05.233
The time spent in Minazuki's
belly

00:13:05.233 --> 00:13:07.233
has accelerated
the healing process.

00:13:07.233 --> 00:13:09.066
Take them to
the relief station

00:13:09.066 --> 00:13:11.266
and monitor them
until they awaken.

00:13:11.266 --> 00:13:12.834
Yes, captain.

00:13:16.633 --> 00:13:18.667
Who is still
up there?

00:13:18.667 --> 00:13:21.600
Such strong
spiritual pressure.

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:22.967
Captain Kuchiki is there,

00:13:22.967 --> 00:13:25.633
battling against the Ryoka
who knocked you out.

00:13:25.633 --> 00:13:26.934
[GASPS]

00:13:26.934 --> 00:13:29.400
The other captains
have all gone elsewhere

00:13:29.400 --> 00:13:32.700
and are now fighting
among themselves.

00:13:32.700 --> 00:13:35.867
Unfortunately, there's nothing
we can do now to stop them.

00:13:38.667 --> 00:13:41.300
Come with me,
Isane.

00:13:41.300 --> 00:13:42.600
Right this way,

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:45.633
there's a certain place
that I would like to visit.

00:13:45.633 --> 00:13:48.433
[WIND WHISTLING]

00:14:03.834 --> 00:14:05.133
That should do it.

00:14:05.133 --> 00:14:07.200
We're pretty far away
from everything.

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:11.233
Far enough to be out of danger.
For a while, at least.

00:14:12.100 --> 00:14:14.800
[PANTING]

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:17.500
Hey, Nanao,
slow poke.

00:14:17.500 --> 00:14:19.100
[GASPS]
You didn't have to leave

00:14:19.100 --> 00:14:20.533
me back there,
captain.

00:14:22.233 --> 00:14:24.033
[GASPS]

00:14:31.166 --> 00:14:35.200
I must say, you got here
quicker than I expected you to.

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:37.300
Chasing children.

00:14:37.300 --> 00:14:39.367
It's been
many years since any

00:14:39.367 --> 00:14:42.834
mere juvenile delinquent
could get away from me.

00:14:42.834 --> 00:14:44.967
Let us finish this!

00:14:44.967 --> 00:14:49.000
But I shall be using
far more than my fists.

00:15:15.300 --> 00:15:18.633
Head Captain
Genruysai Shigekuni Yamamoto.

00:15:18.633 --> 00:15:20.433
Leader of Squad One.

00:15:20.433 --> 00:15:23.166
Head Captain of all
the 13 Court Guard Squads.

00:15:23.166 --> 00:15:25.533
His spiritual pressure is
enormous.

00:15:25.533 --> 00:15:27.133
Even two captains together

00:15:27.133 --> 00:15:29.734
may not be strong enough
to defeat such a man.

00:15:29.734 --> 00:15:31.734
I must help them.

00:15:31.734 --> 00:15:34.300
There's only one thing
I can do.

00:15:35.633 --> 00:15:37.367
[BOOMING]

00:15:37.367 --> 00:15:38.934
[GASPS]

00:15:45.834 --> 00:15:48.300
[GASPING]

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:58.266
[PANTING]

00:16:02.867 --> 00:16:04.667
Listen well.

00:16:04.667 --> 00:16:06.900
Be gone from here!

00:16:09.633 --> 00:16:13.500
I have neither the time
nor the patience

00:16:13.500 --> 00:16:17.367
to teach a mere infant
like you how to breathe.

00:16:26.533 --> 00:16:29.934
Take it easy now,
little Nanao.

00:16:29.934 --> 00:16:31.300
It's gonna be okay.

00:16:36.533 --> 00:16:38.000
I'm so sorry.

00:16:38.000 --> 00:16:41.233
I shouldn't have let you
follow us in the first place.

00:16:48.600 --> 00:16:50.367
I can't believe it.

00:16:50.367 --> 00:16:52.567
All he did was look straight
into my eyes,

00:16:52.567 --> 00:16:55.433
and he completely crushed
my whole being.

00:16:55.433 --> 00:16:59.400
I was so naive to think
I could help

00:16:59.400 --> 00:17:02.100
Captain Ukitake
and my captain.

00:17:02.100 --> 00:17:04.133
I was worried that
they would have trouble

00:17:04.133 --> 00:17:06.233
defeating
the head captain.

00:17:06.233 --> 00:17:08.433
Now I don't think
it's even possible.

00:17:09.667 --> 00:17:13.400
Please be all right,
my captain.

00:17:17.100 --> 00:17:19.500
Your flash step
is impressive.

00:17:19.500 --> 00:17:22.133
Obviously, you've worked
long and hard on it

00:17:22.133 --> 00:17:24.834
to be able to cover
so much ground so quickly.

00:17:25.834 --> 00:17:27.266
Well, thank you.

00:17:27.266 --> 00:17:28.834
YAMAMOTO:
Looking back,

00:17:28.834 --> 00:17:33.533
the two of you always exhibited
exceptional strength.

00:17:33.533 --> 00:17:35.900
You spent too much time
chasing girls, Shunsui,

00:17:35.900 --> 00:17:38.533
and your behavior
was wild.

00:17:38.533 --> 00:17:40.266
But you were intelligent.

00:17:40.266 --> 00:17:42.133
And your ability
to see the truth

00:17:42.133 --> 00:17:45.500
far outshone that of the others
in your class.

00:17:45.500 --> 00:17:47.467
And you, Jushiro,

00:17:47.467 --> 00:17:50.400
you had a weak constitution.

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:52.633
But you more than made up
for it with your daring

00:17:52.633 --> 00:17:53.867
and your popularity.

00:17:53.867 --> 00:17:56.667
Everyone looked up
to you.

00:17:56.667 --> 00:17:59.066
And when it came time
to battle,

00:17:59.066 --> 00:18:01.667
you both defied
the imagination.

00:18:01.667 --> 00:18:04.900
No one else could hold a candle
to either one of you.

00:18:05.934 --> 00:18:08.200
You had such
strong will...

00:18:08.200 --> 00:18:10.200
Training endlessly,

00:18:10.200 --> 00:18:12.800
continuously holding
your strength.

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:14.500
My faith in you
was rewarded when

00:18:14.500 --> 00:18:19.200
you became the first captains of
this Academy, which I created.

00:18:19.200 --> 00:18:21.200
You are my pride
and joy,

00:18:21.200 --> 00:18:23.900
like my own sons.

00:18:23.900 --> 00:18:25.767
I believed in you.

00:18:25.767 --> 00:18:28.367
And though we might have thought
different thoughts,

00:18:28.367 --> 00:18:31.800
I always felt that we walked
the same path.

00:18:39.300 --> 00:18:42.367
Now it appears I was wrong
about you.

00:18:42.367 --> 00:18:45.033
I am deeply disappointed.

00:18:52.734 --> 00:18:55.700
Master Yamamoto.

00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:58.033
Do not say anything.

00:18:58.033 --> 00:19:00.800
The time for words
is long past.

00:19:04.934 --> 00:19:07.266
Draw your swords.

00:19:13.433 --> 00:19:14.800
[GRUNTS]

00:19:15.300 --> 00:19:16.700
[GRUNTING]

00:19:21.734 --> 00:19:24.667
What is the meaning of this,
you two?

00:19:24.667 --> 00:19:27.467
Do not tell me you
that intend to fight me

00:19:27.467 --> 00:19:30.633
without even releasing
your Zanpakuto.

00:19:31.800 --> 00:19:34.467
We're still hoping to avoid
fighting at all,

00:19:34.467 --> 00:19:37.133
old man Yama,
if we can.

00:19:37.133 --> 00:19:38.900
Silence!

00:19:38.900 --> 00:19:40.900
I taught you better
than that.

00:19:40.900 --> 00:19:43.967
You both know that there
can be no forgiveness

00:19:43.967 --> 00:19:46.800
for those who
defy justice.

00:19:46.800 --> 00:19:49.333
And you also taught us
that sometimes

00:19:49.333 --> 00:19:52.900
we must carry out justice
on our own, master.

00:19:52.900 --> 00:19:55.967
And that is the reason we carry
these swords in the first place.

00:19:55.967 --> 00:19:58.300
Is it not,
master?

00:19:58.300 --> 00:20:00.266
Such foolish talk.

00:20:00.266 --> 00:20:02.600
You have no right to decide
for yourselves

00:20:02.600 --> 00:20:03.934
what is right
and wrong.

00:20:03.934 --> 00:20:06.667
It is your duty to accept
the true justice of the world!

00:20:06.667 --> 00:20:09.700
Well, then what is the true
justice of the world, master?

00:20:09.700 --> 00:20:11.633
Who determines
right and wrong?

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:19.967
Did you not
hear me before?

00:20:19.967 --> 00:20:22.166
The time for words...

00:20:22.166 --> 00:20:24.066
Has passed!

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:40.100
[♪♪♪]

00:20:45.133 --> 00:20:46.633
[GASPING]

00:20:51.166 --> 00:20:52.600
Ha-ha-ha.

00:21:55.433 --> 00:21:57.133
[GRUNTING]

00:22:00.700 --> 00:22:04.867
YAMAMOTO:
All things in
the universe turn to ashes.

00:22:06.500 --> 00:22:09.033
Ryujin Jakka!

00:22:20.000 --> 00:22:22.066
[WOMAN SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:23:48.600 --> 00:23:50.367
UKITAKE:
Head Captain Yamamoto,
sir?

00:23:50.367 --> 00:23:53.367
What would I have to do to get
a muscular body like yours?

00:23:53.367 --> 00:23:55.100
KYORAKU:
It is truly magnificent.

00:23:55.100 --> 00:23:57.633
YAMAMOTO:
Well, you must train
each and every day.

00:23:57.633 --> 00:24:00.467
KYORAKU:
Maybe. But it hasn't done
much for your hair.

00:24:00.467 --> 00:24:03.734
YAMAMOTO:
My hair is magnificent,
too!

00:24:03.734 --> 00:24:05.300
Illustrated guide
to Soul Reapers!

00:24:05.300 --> 00:24:06.567
ALL:
Golden!

00:24:06.567 --> 00:24:07.700
[PANTING]

00:24:07.700 --> 00:24:11.400
Take this,
golden cannonball!

00:24:13.033 --> 00:24:14.700
Jinta, home run!

00:24:14.700 --> 00:24:16.166
Let's go,
Karakura King!

00:24:16.166 --> 00:24:17.767
What are you
about to do?

00:24:17.767 --> 00:24:19.500
[YELLING IN JAPANESE]

00:24:19.500 --> 00:24:21.233
[SCREAMING]

00:24:21.233 --> 00:24:23.734
Ugh!
Golden!

00:24:23.734 --> 00:24:26.834
Mission accomplished!
Ha-ha. We did it.

00:24:28.600 --> 00:24:30.133
[YELLING]

00:24:30.133 --> 00:24:31.433
Hey,
what are you looking at?

00:24:31.433 --> 00:24:34.133
Hey, I though this was
the guide to Soul Reapers.

